# Team information

For each team member mentioned at the top of the README.md, we must provide:

- Assigned role(s): PO, PM, Tech Lead, Developers, etc.
- Brief description of their responsibilities.

- Project management:
  - How the team organized their work (methodology, tools used for task management, etc.)
  - Tools used for project management (Github Issues, Treel, etc.)
  - Communicatiion channels used (Discord, Slack, etc.)

- Technical Stack:
  - Frontend technologies and frameworks used
  - Backend technologies and frameworks used
  - Database system and why it was chosen
  - Any other significant technologies or libraries
  - justification for major technical choices.

- Database Schema:
  - Visual representation or description of the database structure.
  - Tables/collections and their relationships
  - key fields and data types

- Feature list:
  - Complete list of implemented features
  - Which team member(s) worked on each feature
  - Brief description of each feature's functionality

- Modules:
  - List of all chosen modules (Major and Minor)
  - Point Calculation (Major = 2pts, Minor = 1pt)
  - Justification for the choice of modules, especially for custom ones
  - how each modules was implemented and integrated into the project
  - Which team member(s) worked on each module

